| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2658 — Recovery Inhibition (medusa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 33268f85-cb34-52b3-9da5-4a0fe35fa21a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
